oups—most often the rich and powerful—entrench themselves over time and begin demanding privileges from the state. — location: <a href=\"kindle://book?action=open&#x26;asin=B00457X7VI&#x26;location=535\" class=\"prose-lg text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline transition-colors duration-200\">535</a> ^ref-16822</p>\n<svg class=\"mx-auto my-8 w-full max-w-prose\" height=\"1\">\n  <line x1=\"0\" y1=\"0\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"0\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-dasharray=\"2,4\" />\n</svg>",
